            How to create account on phonepay -
          </h2>
          <h4>Follow these steps -</h4>
          <ol>
            <li> Download the app from the Google Play Store or Apple App Store.</li>
            <li>After downloading the app, open the app and verify your mobile number. (Be sure that the mobile number you entered should be the same one registered with your bank account).</li>
            <li>Enter all the required details (Name, email address and set your 4-digit password and activate your wallet.</li>
            <li>Tap on creating new Virtual Private Address (VPA).</li>
            <li> Select your bank account to link, the app will automatically fetch the details.</li>
            <li>Confirm your bank details.</li>
           
          </ol>

